                  "name": "aboutP1",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "I paint intuitively, allowing color and movement to guide the process. My work explores emotions, memories and inner landscapes that are difficult to describe with words.",
